========
:display mark

	to display all marks currenly set, on form `(row,col)', 
	as :set ruler

	should produce

	a (6,4)
	b (3,4)
	...

========
v,V like elvis

	visually selects text, for yanking, deleting, etc... 

	V selects on a line basis
	v selects on a character basis

========
[a .. [z 
]a .. ]z 

	[x starts recording every keystroke on buffer x, until
	a ]x is done

	actually, the ]x is does not need to specify the x at all

	idea: 

		[x	starts recording 
		[. 	stops recording

	saves all ]x for future use
